snippet.title: Quadruzzle On Steam
snippet.description:
Quadruzzle is a multifaceted puzzle game that combines 4 word puzzles along with the popular 15 puzzle.  Test your knowledge, vocabulary, spelling, memory and spatial logic skills, with this daily puzzle solver.  Available on Steam December 1st 2023.

Music track: Funky by Waesto
Source: https://freetouse.com/music
